data.description: Wow! Talk about a charmer. This 2 bedroom house is situated on two lots, in Brookside, and has a completely updated kitchen AND bathroom. The first floor feels very spacious, open and bright. The beautifully remodeled kitchen includes new cabinetry with soft close doors, crown molding, tiled backsplash, a farmhouse sink and stainless steel appliances. Did I mention the granite countertops plus the impressive island positioned in the dining area. The updated laminate flooring on the first floor adds to the generous list of updates to this cape cod. First floor features a large living room, kitchen and dining area. On the second floor are the two bedrooms and full bathroom. Bathroom is updated with a nice vanity and tile flooring.
